WEBVTT

00:01:09.599 --> 00:01:11.040
Ruochu, you're looking at...

00:01:11.040 --> 00:01:13.000
I was just about to explain this to you

00:01:13.079 --> 00:01:13.920
It's all a misunderstanding

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:15.480
These photos are all a setup to frame me

00:01:15.480 --> 00:01:16.799
Ms. Wen's mother is critically ill

00:01:16.799 --> 00:01:19.200
Brother Liang and I went to find foreign experts for her

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:21.200
She got too emotional, that's why she acted that way

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:22.439
It's not what you think at all

00:01:23.079 --> 00:01:23.879
Is that so?

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:25.280
Really

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:28.599
Alright, I believe you

00:01:31.159 --> 00:01:33.040
I know you're not that kind of person

00:01:33.719 --> 00:01:35.599
Besides, I was just looking at these photos

00:01:35.680 --> 00:01:38.000
Look, the camera angle is way too deliberate

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:40.079
And this one looks just like a collage

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:41.519
The edges are all blurry

00:01:44.359 --> 00:01:45.359
I thought you were going to confront me

00:01:45.359 --> 00:01:46.760
Or even give me the cold shoulder

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:47.760
I was scared to death

00:01:47.760 --> 00:01:48.879
I ran over here immediately to...

00:01:48.920 --> 00:01:50.560
I was afraid you'd see them and misunderstand

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:51.640
After all, I spent...

00:01:51.640 --> 00:01:52.920
...at Honghai's Computer School...

00:01:52.959 --> 00:01:54.680
...a whole summer with you

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:56.200
You think I can't spot a trick like this?

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:57.680
Besides

00:01:57.719 --> 00:02:00.079
I know very well what kind of person you are

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:02.359
Look, back when you first built the website...

00:02:02.359 --> 00:02:03.560
...you encountered hackers

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:04.599
Buying the amusement park...

00:02:04.599 --> 00:02:06.519
...and big companies looking for trouble

00:02:06.640 --> 00:02:08.639
Did you offend someone again this time?

00:02:10.719 --> 00:02:11.800
As long as you believe in me...

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:13.560
...there's no problem that can't be solved

00:02:13.879 --> 00:02:14.680
Enough about that

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:16.400
I'll handle it

00:02:17.919 --> 00:02:18.599
I believe you

00:02:23.919 --> 00:02:25.159
You'll definitely handle it well

00:02:25.159 --> 00:02:25.800
Yeah

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:36.599
Ruochu, after we finish our elective class...

00:02:36.599 --> 00:02:38.400
...we'll celebrate your birthday tonight

00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:56.800
Stinky Chen Fan

00:03:13.479 --> 00:03:14.439
Hello, Brother Honghai

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:15.439
Ruochu

00:03:16.919 --> 00:03:17.800
Happy Birthday

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:19.919
Thank you, Brother Honghai

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:22.800
You've remembered my birthday since we were kids

00:03:22.879 --> 00:03:24.199
I heard from your mom...

00:03:24.199 --> 00:03:25.360
...that you're not coming home for your birthday this year?

00:03:25.919 --> 00:03:26.960
I'm not going back

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:28.400
Chen Fan...

00:03:28.400 --> 00:03:30.479
...didn't he just finish with the club business?

00:03:30.919 --> 00:03:32.159
Now he's being framed again

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.159
I'm staying to keep him company

00:03:35.759 --> 00:03:36.719
I heard about that

00:03:36.759 --> 00:03:38.680
They say there are photos, right?

00:03:38.719 --> 00:03:39.719
Those are all fake

00:03:39.719 --> 00:03:41.240
The department has already cleared it up

00:03:41.479 --> 00:03:42.879
What Chen Fan's character is like...

00:03:43.199 --> 00:03:44.080
...and how he treats me...

00:03:44.439 --> 00:03:45.719
...I know in my heart

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:47.840
Good

00:03:48.319 --> 00:03:49.400
Thank you, Brother Honghai

00:03:55.319 --> 00:03:57.400
Su Ruochu, 19 years old

00:03:59.000 --> 00:03:59.800
Be happy

00:04:03.800 --> 00:04:04.479
Ruochu

00:04:05.199 --> 00:04:06.639
Hasn't your boyfriend come to find you yet?

00:04:08.319 --> 00:04:09.800
It's okay, you go to the library first

00:04:09.800 --> 00:04:11.120
I want to take a walk alone

00:04:11.759 --> 00:04:13.120
Do you really not need me to keep you company?

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:15.159
It's fine, didn't you have homework to finish?

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:15.960
You go ahead

00:04:16.399 --> 00:04:17.759
Alright, then I'm off

00:04:17.759 --> 00:04:18.120
Bye bye

00:04:18.120 --> 00:04:18.680
Bye bye

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:36.319
Sorry, sorry

00:04:36.319 --> 00:04:36.959
It's okay, it's okay

00:04:37.920 --> 00:04:38.720
Thank you

00:04:39.279 --> 00:04:39.920
Thank you

00:04:39.920 --> 00:04:40.240
Here

00:04:41.199 --> 00:04:41.800
Thank you

00:04:42.319 --> 00:04:43.959
Su Ruochu, Happy Birthday

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:46.199
This isn't me

00:04:55.360 --> 00:04:56.120
Su Ruochu

00:04:57.600 --> 00:04:58.360
Happy Birthday

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:00.639
Thank you

00:05:04.839 --> 00:05:05.720
Su Ruochu

00:05:06.519 --> 00:05:07.399
Happy Birthday

00:05:07.959 --> 00:05:08.680
Thank you

00:05:34.920 --> 00:05:36.279
Happy Birthday

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:38.000
You prepared all of this?

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:41.879
I just wanted to give you a surprise

00:05:57.279 --> 00:05:59.759
Happy birthday to you

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:01.879
Happy birthday to you

00:06:01.879 --> 00:06:04.439
Happy birthday to you

00:06:04.439 --> 00:06:07.000
Happy birthday to you

00:06:08.879 --> 00:06:11.439
Happy Birthday

00:06:22.600 --> 00:06:23.240
Come.

00:06:25.399 --> 00:06:26.160
This is...

00:06:27.800 --> 00:06:28.519
our home.

00:06:29.199 --> 00:06:30.439
You rented a place?

00:06:30.519 --> 00:06:31.279
I bought it.

00:06:31.279 --> 00:06:32.399
Bought it?

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:33.399
When did you buy it?

00:06:33.399 --> 00:06:34.519
Why didn't you tell me?

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:36.879
That's not important.

00:06:37.759 --> 00:06:38.600
Do you like it?

00:06:40.160 --> 00:06:40.959
I like it.

00:06:43.519 --> 00:06:45.040
But it's so strange.

00:06:45.160 --> 00:06:46.800
It's clearly my first time here.

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:49.040
But I have a feeling of déjà vu.

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:49.959
It's just...

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:52.000
especially this balcony.

00:06:52.519 --> 00:06:53.879
I feel like I've been here before.

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:55.879
Chen Fan.

00:06:56.279 --> 00:06:57.800
Look at all these things you got.

00:06:57.879 --> 00:06:59.279
It's such a waste.

00:06:59.879 --> 00:07:01.319
Even if you made money,

00:07:01.319 --> 00:07:02.759
you shouldn't be this wasteful.

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:04.480
Fresh flowers aren't practical.

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:05.439
Might as well buy two bottles...

00:07:05.439 --> 00:07:05.959
...of soy sauce.

00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:09.240
How did you know what I was going to say?

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:12.199
Because you used to say that often.

00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:14.000
Used to?

00:07:14.600 --> 00:07:15.519
Often?

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.720
Ruochu, happy birthday.

00:07:24.199 --> 00:07:25.439
When I have money in the future,

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:26.519
I'll definitely buy a...

00:07:26.519 --> 00:07:27.839
...cake bigger than this for you.

00:07:28.560 --> 00:07:29.240
I believe in you.

00:07:30.480 --> 00:07:31.800
You will definitely succeed.

00:07:32.160 --> 00:07:34.240
Then tell me your wish first.

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:39.720
I hope that in the future we...

00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:41.519
have a really big house.

00:07:42.120 --> 00:07:44.079
A house filled with fresh flowers.

00:07:45.120 --> 00:07:46.800
I hope we'll be together forever.

00:07:49.720 --> 00:07:50.839
Blow out the candles.

00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:54.959
Happy birthday.

00:07:57.759 --> 00:07:58.959
Thank you, Chen Fan.

00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:01.680
This is truly the most romantic...

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:03.279
...and special birthday I've ever had.

00:08:06.839 --> 00:08:07.879
Wait for me.

00:08:14.879 --> 00:08:15.920
This is your gift.

00:08:35.720 --> 00:08:36.799
Ruochu.

00:08:36.799 --> 00:08:38.279
I once had a dream.

00:08:38.879 --> 00:08:40.480
In the dream, we didn't make it to the end.

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:43.039
But now I've woken up.

00:08:43.080 --> 00:08:44.720
This time, I can't lose you again.

00:08:45.159 --> 00:08:46.240
I want to be with you...

00:08:46.559 --> 00:08:48.360
...to see the world's splendor...

00:08:49.080 --> 00:08:50.080
...and the brilliant galaxy.

00:08:50.600 --> 00:08:51.399
Will you?

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:56.279
Yes.

00:10:08.200 --> 00:10:09.799
Did you prepare these too?

00:10:11.320 --> 00:10:12.080
No.

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:13.240
Beijing won.

00:10:13.519 --> 00:10:15.519
The Olympic bid was successful!

00:10:16.840 --> 00:10:17.320
It succeeded!

00:10:17.360 --> 00:10:18.240
The Olympic bid was successful!

00:10:20.279 --> 00:10:22.399
Then let's go watch the Olympic Games in seven years.

00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:23.360
Okay.

00:10:47.159 --> 00:10:47.840
Ruochu.

00:10:58.679 --> 00:10:59.240
Ruochu.

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:00.799
Ruochu.

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:06.240
Chen Fan.

00:11:07.240 --> 00:11:08.039
Let's break up.